And "perform the billing operation [...] including but not limited to the

about fulfilling bank transactions, but I'm not sure. 

The other mysterious phrase is:

our sole discretion, determine that it is necessary to enforce compliance 
with our Terms of Service or to protect our service, Site, customers or 
others."
